# Grid areas

> The hidden grid property that most developers don't know exists

## What are they?

Once we have our grid we can then template out some areas and assign children to them

```
.🎁 {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-areas:
    "a b b"
    "a b b"
    "a . ."
    "a c c";
  grid-auto-rows: 100px;
}

.🍌 {
  grid-area: a;
}

.🥥 {
  grid-area: b;
}

.🍆 {
  grid-area: c;
}
```

