It's a very nice implementation but look what happens when the circles get really clode together 😝

There is another intresting thing you can do with grid areas.
Multiple children can share the same area 😲

```
.🟣 {
  grid-template-areas: "circle";
}

.🧒 {
  grid-area: circle;
}

.🧒:nth-child(1) {
  place-self: start center;
}

.🧒:nth-child(2) {
  place-self: center start;
}

.🧒:nth-child(3) {
  place-self: center;
}

.🧒:nth-child(4) {
  place-self: center end;
}

.🧒:nth-child(5) {
  place-self: end center;
}
```

